This @aorus_official sponsored build is almost done!

Had some fun with the new Razer Tomahawk case and built a Chroma RGB battlestation setup for Razercon 2020! Is this enough RGB for you or do you need even more?

Main specs:

Razer Tomahawk ATX case
Intel i9 10900k
RTX 3080 Founders edition
32 GB of XPG DDR4
4TB WD Black AN1500 Pcie storage
MSI MPG Z490 Gaming Carbon Wifi
MSI MAG CoreLiquid 360R
Thermaltake PRORGB 850

#pcmr #razer #razertomahawk #pcmasterrace
